-- Special words
to = that
wo = what
--

mu, mi = I/me, my
yu, yi = you, your
tu, ti
malu, mali = we, our
yalu, yalu
talu, tali = they, their

a: active
e: pasive
u: noun
i: adjective/adverb
o: preposition

bazita sur la skriba formo, mi forigas literojn
vorto ne finiĝu per konsonanto

yeso: jes (affirmative)
no: ne
(? maybe change to yesi, ni)
nu: mal

pi: past
vi: future
nowi: nun
gi : imperfect
di : perfect

? Remove r in roots if followed by a consonent ?

