to attempt - testa
to talk - speka
to speak - speka
tool - tolu
language - spektolu
front - nubaku
back - baku
place (time or space) - atu
place (space) - plasu
stead (place for a function) - stedu
theme - temu
exception - ekseptu
duration - wilu
cause - kaso
way - wayu
origin - fromu
past - pastu
future - nupastu
now - nowu
array - aru
group - aru
word - wordu
sentence - wordaru

I - mu
to must - musta
to do - maka
to make - maka
